[%@lib@member shl[!simd]]
[%@lib@member shr[!simd]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral VX, [[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral VS>
  constexpr VX shl(const VX& x, const VS& s) noexcept;
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral VX, [[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral VS>
  constexpr VX shr(const VX& x, const VS& s) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] Each of [`VX::value_type] and [`VS::value_type] is a signed or unsigned integer type ([#basic.fundamental]),
[:zh_CN] 类型 [`VX::value_type] 和 [`VS::value_type] 都是有符号或无符号整数类型（[#basic.fundamental]），
[item]
[:en] [`VX::size() == VS::size()] is [`true], and
[:zh_CN] [`VX::size() == VS::size()] 为 [`true]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`sizeof(typename VX::value_type) == sizeof(typename VS::value_type)] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`sizeof(typename VX::value_type) == sizeof(typename VS::value_type)] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:returns]
[:en] A [`basic_vec] object where the [$i^\text{th}] element is initialized to
the result of [`[^bit-func](x`[[$i]`], s`[[$i]`])]
for all [$i] in the range [=range(0,VX::size())], where [`[^bit-func]] is the
corresponding scalar function from [?libheader bit].
[:zh_CN] 一个 [`basic_vec] 对象，其中对于范围 [=range(0,VX::size())] 中的每个 [$i]，
其第 [$i] 个元素以 [`[^bit-func](x`[[$i]`], s`[[$i]`])]
的结果初始化，其中 [`[^bit-func]] 是 [?libheader bit] 中的对应标量函数。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member shl[!simd]]
[%@lib@member shr[!simd]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral V, class S>
  constexpr V shl(const V& x, S s) noexcept;
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral V, class S>
  constexpr V shr(const V& x, S s) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[:en] Each of [`VX::value_type] and [`S] is a signed or unsigned integer type ([#basic.fundamental]).
[:zh_CN] 类型 [`VX::value_type] 和 [`S] 都是有符号或无符号整数类型（[#basic.fundamental]）。

[para:returns]
[:en] A [`basic_vec] object where the [$i^\text{th}] element is initialized to
the result of [`[^bit-func](x`[[$i]`], s)] for all [$i] in the range [=range(0,VX::size())],
where [`[^bit-func]] is the corresponding scalar function from [?libheader bit].
[:zh_CN] 一个 [`basic_vec] 对象，其中对于范围 [=range(0,VX::size())] 中的每个 [$i]，
其第 [$i] 个元素以 [`[^bit-func](x`[[$i]`], s)] 的结果初始化，
其中 [`[^bit-func]] 是 [?libheader bit] 中的对应标量函数。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member rotl[!simd]]
[%@lib@member rotr[!simd]]
[%@lib@member bit_repeat[!simd]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-vec-type V0, [[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-vec-type V1>
  constexpr V0 rotl(const V0& v0, const V1& v1) noexcept;
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-vec-type V0, [[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-vec-type V1>
  constexpr V0 rotr(const V0& v0, const V1& v1) noexcept;
template<[[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral V0, [[redoc("*:c>")]]simd-integral V1>
  constexpr V0 bit_repeat(const V0& v0, const V1& v1);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] The type [`V0::value_type] is an unsigned integer type ([#basic.fundamental]),
[:zh_CN] 类型 [`V0::value_type] 是一种无符号整数类型（[#basic.fundamental]），
[item]
[:en] The type [`V1::value_type] models [`:c integral],
[:zh_CN] 类型 [`V1::value_type] 构成 [`:c integral]，
[item]
[:en] [`V0::size() == V1::size()] is [`true], and
[:zh_CN] [`V0::size() == V1::size()] 为 [`true]，并且
[item]
[:en] [`sizeof(typename V0::value_type) == sizeof(typename V1::value_type)] is [`true].
[:zh_CN] [`sizeof(typename V0::value_type) == sizeof(typename V1::value_type)] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:expects]
[:en] For [`bit_repeat], [`v1`[[$i]`] > 0] is [`true] for all [$i] in the range [=range(0,V0::size())].
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`bit_repeat]，[`v1`[[$i]`] > 0] 对于范围 [=range(0,V0::size())] 中的所有 [$i] 均为 [`true]。

[para:returns]
[:en] A [`basic_vec] object where the [$i^\text{th}] element is initialized to
the result of [`[^bit-func](v0`[[$i]`], static_cast<int>(v1`[[$i]`]))]
for all [$i] in the range [=range(0,V0::size())], where [`[^bit-func]] is the
corresponding scalar function from [?libheader bit].
[:zh_CN] 一个 [`basic_vec] 对象，其中对于范围 [=range(0,V0::size())] 中的每个 [$i]，
其第 [$i] 个元素以 [`[^bit-func](v0`[[$i]`], static_cast<int>(v1`[[$i]`]))]
的结果初始化，其中 [`[^bit-func]] 是 [?libheader bit] 中的对应标量函数。

[para:remarks]
[:en] A function call expression that violates the precondition in the [=expects]
element is not a core constant expression ([#expr.const.core]).
[:zh_CN] 违反 [=expects] 要素中的前条件的函数调用表达式不是核心常量表达式（[#expr.const.core]）。
[div:end]

